        "evidence": "<p dir=\"ltr\">A = (8.5 x INR) + (AST,&nbsp;U/L&nbsp;/ 35)</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">B = (Platelet count, x&nbsp;10&sup3;/&micro;L&nbsp;/ 150) + (BUN, mg/dL / 20) + (Hemoglobin, g/dL / 15)</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">EVendo Score = (A / B) + 1 (if ascites present)</p>",
        "facts": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Interpretation:</p>\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"94\" /><col width=\"138\" /><col width=\"216\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>EVendo Score</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Probability of finding varices*</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Recommendation</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&le;3.90</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&lt;5%**</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Expectant management</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&gt;3.90</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ge;5%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Endoscopy</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>*Any esophageal varices or varices needing treatment.</p>\n<p>**95.1% sensitivity, 95.8% NPV.</p>\n<p>From <a href=\"https://www.cghjournal.org/article/S1542-3565(19)30072-2/pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Dong 2019</a>.</p>",
